I remember doing something along the lines of  ```{% if topic %}
&lt;h3&gt;Posts about &lt;span class="tag-listing-title"&gt;{{ topic|replace('-', ' ')}}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;style&gt;
    .tag-listing-title {
        text-transform: capitalize;
    }
&lt;/style&gt;
{% endif %}``` as well. Great idea on `|title` Jon, even better
